Reasoning: The paper discusses a new Python-based library for automating the management and online publication of scientific software and data. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and computer engineering (cs.CE). The library also deals with data management and publication, which could fall under digital libraries (cs.DL) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the integration of the library into an open-source computational fluid dynamics package could also relate to programming languages (cs.PL).
